00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:28,480
Gu Nian, having a nice chat?

568
00:29:29,040 --> 00:29:30,680
If you're done chatting, come help me catch fish in the kitchen.

569
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,740
There's a ton of work waiting for you.

570
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,000
Professor Zhuo,

571
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:36,460
I have to go catch fish now.

572
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,210
He's impressed with me.

573
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:40,680
He really appreciates me.

574
00:29:57,400 --> 00:29:57,930
Darling,

575
00:29:58,600 --> 00:29:59,400
most of the guests have arrived,

576
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,160
we should go over there now.

577
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,320
Okay, let's go.

578
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:02,730
You look beautiful.

579
00:30:05,360 --> 00:30:06,320
Hello.

580
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,080
Xuwei,

581
00:30:08,360 --> 00:30:10,520
you look gorgeous today. Congratulations!

582
00:30:10,520 --> 00:30:11,320
Thank you.

583
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:13,280
Why are you still wearing your school uniform today?

584
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,400
You two chat.

585
00:30:14,840 --> 00:30:16,200
I lost my suitcase.

586
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,160
Let me introduce you,

587
00:30:18,160 --> 00:30:19,800
this is my bridesmaid for today.

588
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:20,680
Hello.

589
00:30:21,360 --> 00:30:22,280
It's you.

590
00:30:22,520 --> 00:30:23,640
Oh, it's you.

591
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:26,360
Is your hand feeling better?

592
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:26,880
Much better,

593
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,000
it doesn't hurt anymore.

594
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:30,120
You two know each other?

595
00:30:31,600 --> 00:30:32,440
Lin Yao,

596
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:33,520
while you were away,

597
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:35,840
Zhuopeng has put so much effort into Lizhong Study Abroad,

598
00:30:35,840 --> 00:30:36,440
look,

599
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:39,240
he's even using my wedding to interview students.

600
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:40,240
In the next couple of days,

601
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:41,880
pay attention to your arm,

602
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,610
you can't be careless about it.

603
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:45,800
He is my fiancé.

604
00:30:46,120 --> 00:30:47,980
Lin Yao is really his girlfriend?

605
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:50,160
You're Lin Yao.

606
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:58,840
You're a student from Lizhong Study Abroad?

607
00:30:58,840 --> 00:31:00,500
You can't possibly be Lin Yao.

608
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:03,920
Gu Nian.

609
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:05,880
Gu Nian.

610
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:08,680
Professor Conway has some more questions for you,

611
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:09,680
come on, let's go.

612
00:31:10,360 --> 00:31:11,690
Is she your girlfriend?

613
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,000
Yes.

614
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,840
That guy who bumped into me last time

615
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:16,080
said he was her fiancé.

616
00:31:16,080 --> 00:31:17,080
Gu Nian.

617
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:24,920
I'm sorry, Xu Wei,

618
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,120
I'm not feeling well,

619
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:27,600
I need to leave now. Sorry.

620
00:31:28,320 --> 00:31:29,320
Lin Yao.

621
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:32,360
I'm sorry.

622
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:33,920
Lin Yao.

623
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,600
Darling, are you okay?

624
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:51,680
Gu Nian.

625
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:53,200
Come with me for a moment.

626
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:59,690
To have an affair discovered like this is really something.

627
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:03,080
Lin Yao.

628
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:04,840
Stop following me,

629
00:32:04,840 --> 00:32:06,280
haven't I been humiliated enough?

630
00:32:06,280 --> 00:32:06,640
I'm sorry,

631
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:09,040
I completely forgot she had met you before.

632
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:13,360
You knew she had met me?

633
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:17,680
You've known about me from Gu Nian all along

634
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:18,800
and kept it from me.

635
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,520
I didn't learn it from Gu Nian.

636
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:22,960
I saw it myself.

637
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,620
It was just a coincidence.

638
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:31,000
That day when you had the accident

639
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:32,240
when you hit Gu Nian,

640
00:32:33,360 --> 00:32:35,480
I saw you with him with my own eyes.

641
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,360
You've known since then?

642
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:39,120
I wasn't sure it was you.

643
00:32:39,120 --> 00:32:40,520
Don't say anything more.

644
00:32:41,080 --> 00:32:43,340
I was planning to propose to you that day.

645
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,400
Lin Yao.

646
00:32:47,280 --> 00:32:48,940
What I really want to say is...

647
00:32:56,360 --> 00:32:57,680
What did you just say?

648
00:32:58,840 --> 00:33:00,280
Those earrings

649
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:02,620
are what Lin Yao really likes.

650
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:04,480
Zhuo Peng,

651
00:33:05,320 --> 00:33:07,000
what are you trying to say?

652
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:09,640
What you want to give, Lin Yao doesn't need.

653
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:11,000
What Lin Yao needs,

654
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:13,120
you can't give even if you wanted to.

655
00:33:13,120 --> 00:33:14,650
What I really want to say is,

656
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:15,960
let's break up.

657
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:17,760
Break up?

658
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:19,860
Although all these years,

659
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,800
I've been unwilling to admit it,

660
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:24,370
but I'm truly not the right person for you.

661
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:25,280
Not right?

662
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:26,720
Lin Yao,

663
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,840
I know you want a privileged

664
00:33:28,840 --> 00:33:29,840
and stable life.

665
00:33:30,360 --> 00:33:31,280
But me,

666
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:32,940
I'm used to being idle,

667
00:33:33,240 --> 00:33:35,840
I can't be as ambitious as you want,

668
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:37,700
I can't give you the life you want.

669
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,920
I don't want to hold you back anymore.

670
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:40,280
Zhuo Peng.

671
00:33:40,280 --> 00:33:41,680
Don't say anything more,

672
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:43,320
I've already made up my mind.

673
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,520
But I have one request.

674
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:53,440
Could we wait until

675
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:55,200
after Xu Wei's wedding

676
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:57,000
to tell our friends?

677
00:33:57,520 --> 00:33:58,880
The wedding is coming soon,

678
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:01,080
and she's asked you to be her bridesmaid.

679
00:34:01,080 --> 00:34:02,540
On such a joyous occasion,

680
00:34:02,800 --> 00:34:05,130
could we go together and be happy about it?

681
00:34:05,600 --> 00:34:07,880
Don't let our friends worry about us,

682
00:34:07,880 --> 00:34:09,940
don't give them a chance to bother us.

683
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:16,360
I had the ring ready.

684
00:34:16,440 --> 00:34:18,040
I was going to propose to you.

685
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:22,290
But I broke up with you instead.

686
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:26,880
Because I didn't want to put you in a difficult position,

687
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:29,239
didn't want you to be the one to say it first.

688
00:34:29,239 --> 00:34:30,400
You think everything you did

689
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:31,460
was for my own good,

690
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:33,719
so good that you even broke up with me on my behalf,

691
00:34:33,719 --> 00:34:36,280
and only I, Lin Yao, am an ungrateful liar.

692
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:37,840
You think you're so noble, don't you?

693
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:38,600
Lin Yao.

694
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,280
I don't know why you're saying this.

695
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:42,000
You know that's not what I think.

696
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:43,860
You've known how I feel all along,

697
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:45,239
yet you pretended not to notice,

698
00:34:45,239 --> 00:34:47,040
watching me struggle with anxiety and confusion.

699
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:48,370
Was that amusing to you?

700
00:34:48,719 --> 00:34:49,800
Please stop saying these things

701
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:51,360
that hurt us both.

702
00:34:51,880 --> 00:34:53,340
Let me tell you, Zhuopeng,

703
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:55,600
you were absolutely right that day.

704
00:34:55,600 --> 00:34:56,679
I chose someone else

705
00:34:56,679 --> 00:34:59,280
because you couldn't give me the life I wanted.

706
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,240
You've made your choice,

707
00:35:04,240 --> 00:35:05,360
I won't blame you.

708
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,400
But I just hope you can give

709
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:10,130
our decade-long relationship

710
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:12,330
at least one beautiful memory.

711
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:13,680
Is there any left?

712
00:35:14,560 --> 00:35:16,160
All the beautiful things between us

713
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:17,120
were just now,

714
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:19,200
in front of all our friends,

715
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:21,080
completely destroyed.

716
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:42,180
That's enough.

717
00:35:42,720 --> 00:35:44,720
Go wash the dishes in the back now.

718
00:35:45,600 --> 00:35:46,040
I...

719
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:47,170
What do you mean 'I'?

720
00:35:47,240 --> 00:35:49,200
Haven't you caused enough trouble already?

721
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:50,760
I didn't mean to cause trouble.

722
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:52,360
I was just telling the truth.

723
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:54,280
Do you realize what you've said?

724
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:56,480
But she really didn't tell me she was Lin Yao,

725
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:58,340
and she even said she had a fiancé.

726
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:02,080
Fine, let's say everything you said is true.

727
00:36:02,080 --> 00:36:03,760
Yes, what you said is true,

728
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:06,760
but shouldn't you consider the right time and place to expose someone?

729
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,240
Look at the mess you've created.

730
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:09,880
Lin Yao couldn't stay and ran off,

731
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:11,640
and Zhuo Peng went after her, didn't he?

732
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:12,480
Now at Xu Wei's wedding,

733
00:36:12,480 --> 00:36:13,600
they can't even find the bridesmaid.

734
00:36:13,600 --> 00:36:14,560
I swear,

735
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:17,720
dealing with a stubborn kid like you...

736
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:18,280
I'm just

737
00:36:18,720 --> 00:36:20,380
wasting my breath, honestly.

738
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:22,040
Just go do your work.

739
00:36:22,520 --> 00:36:23,520
But if Lin Yao really did something

740
00:36:23,520 --> 00:36:25,360
to hurt Professor Zhuo,

741
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,890
I think he deserves to know.

742
00:36:29,680 --> 00:36:32,400
I know you two have a close teacher-student relationship.

743
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:32,920
Let me tell you,

744
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,440
Zhuo Peng sacrificed himself just so you could meet Professor Conway,

745
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:35,360
he put everything on the line for you,

746
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:37,090
so think about that for a while.

747
00:37:10,040 --> 00:37:13,600
What do you think is really going on between Zhuo Peng and Lin Yao?

748
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:15,600
They've been together for so many years,

749
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:17,330
what could Lin Yao be thinking?

750
00:37:17,680 --> 00:37:19,360
Are you really surprised about what happened with Lin Yao?

751
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,000
I actually think it's quite normal.

752
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:21,800
To be honest,

753
00:37:22,040 --> 00:37:23,440
I've always wondered

754
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:25,640
how Zhuo Peng ended up with Lin Yao in the first place.

755
00:37:25,640 --> 00:37:28,300
They're completely different types of people.

756
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,080
Besides,

757
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:31,240
when I first met Lin Yao,

758
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:33,570
I could tell she was really something.

759
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:34,560
Her eyes were

760
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:36,360
full of ambition and desire.

761
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:38,040
And another thing,

762
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:39,560
she founded Lizhong Study Abroad all by herself,

763
00:37:39,560 --> 00:37:40,890
she's such a go-getter.

764
00:37:43,120 --> 00:37:45,040
Could Lizhong Study Abroad be what it is today without Zhuo Peng?

765
00:37:45,040 --> 00:37:47,000
Do you know how much Zhuo Peng sacrificed for that company,

766
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,200
how much he suffered!

767
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:50,000
You can't look at it that way.

768
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,400
People always aim higher,

769
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:53,280
maybe she found a better option.

770
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:55,360
So what you're saying is,

771
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,600
if someone finds a better option,

772
00:37:56,600 --> 00:37:58,320
it's okay to betray your relationship?

773
00:37:58,320 --> 00:37:58,920
No,

774
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,720
I was just making a comparison.

775
00:38:00,720 --> 00:38:01,600
What comparison?

776
00:38:01,600 --> 00:38:02,520
Besides, we don't even know

777
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:03,920
what the truth really is.

778
00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:06,200
Maybe in a few days they'll get past this rough patch

779
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:08,320
and make up again.

780
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:09,920
You can forgive betrayal?

781
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,250
I definitely couldn't.

782
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:16,240
What if it were me?

783
00:38:17,080 --> 00:38:18,320
Are you planning to betray me?

784
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:20,050
What's wrong with finding out?

785
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:22,080
Keep driving! Keep driving!

786
00:38:22,080 --> 00:38:23,600
No, that's wrong! Wrong!

787
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,260
I'll bite you to death.

788
00:39:00,040 --> 00:39:01,240
How could we possibly not get married?

789
00:39:01,240 --> 00:39:02,970
How could we possibly break up?

790
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:05,080
How could she possibly reject me?

791
00:39:05,080 --> 00:39:06,840
We've known each other since childhood,

792
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:07,960
been together for so many years.

793
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:09,000
Bro, where does all this confidence come from?

794
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:10,120
This isn't confidence,

795
00:39:10,120 --> 00:39:13,180
it's that Lin Yao and I have a very stable relationship.

796
00:39:21,040 --> 00:39:23,960
Although I haven't known Lin Yao for long,

797
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:26,560
I know exactly what she likes,

798
00:39:26,560 --> 00:39:28,220
enough for me to accompany her

799
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:31,240
to every art gallery and museum she wants to visit.

800
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:34,480
This kind of happiness with you

801
00:39:34,480 --> 00:39:36,280
hasn't happened for a long time.

802
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:38,840
You and Lin Yao take photos to commemorate every year.

803
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:40,440
She doesn't even like

804
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:43,240
these things, but you've never noticed, have you?

805
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:45,160
Lin Yao is such a nice girl

806
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:48,960
who's been suppressing her true personality just to please you.

807
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:52,840
Surprise?

808
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,760
Every year, for all those holidays and anniversaries,

809
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:58,320
it's always the same routine,

810
00:39:58,320 --> 00:40:00,040
what kind of surprise is that?

811
00:40:00,240 --> 00:40:02,040
No matter what holiday or anniversary,

812
00:40:02,040 --> 00:40:03,560
it's always the exact same thing:

813
00:40:03,560 --> 00:40:05,360
flowers, cake, photos,

814
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,760
you haven't even changed the location.

815
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:08,440
Man on the left, woman on the right.

816
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:09,240
What makes you so confident

817
00:40:09,240 --> 00:40:11,440
that Lin Yao will definitely marry you?

818
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:14,040
You're pushing Lin Yao into

819
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:15,970
an even more difficult situation.

820
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:18,360
Mom.

821
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:19,800
What's wrong?

822
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:21,880
You sound upset.

823
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:24,680
No, everything's fine.

824
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:26,520
How was the interview?

825
00:41:26,520 --> 00:41:27,400
Did you do well?

826
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:30,840
It went well, really well.

827
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:31,760
Very smoothly.

828
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:33,400
That's good to hear.

829
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:35,840
So you can come back tomorrow with peace of mind.

830
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:38,300
Your dad and I will pick you up at the airport.

831
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:39,160
Got it.

832
00:41:39,520 --> 00:41:40,280
Bye-bye.

833
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:51,800
Coming!

834
00:42:07,440 --> 00:42:08,360
Don't clean up.

835
00:42:08,560 --> 00:42:09,600
Why is your place such a mess?

836
00:42:09,600 --> 00:42:10,930
There's nowhere to sit.

837
00:42:11,040 --> 00:42:12,600
Just tell me what you want.

838
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:15,840
If it's not convenient,

839
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:17,370
we can talk somewhere else.

840
00:42:17,760 --> 00:42:18,480
I know

841
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:20,810
you wouldn't be comfortable here anyway.

842
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:25,560
Wait while I put something on.
